    "Eduardo Vivas is a pre-IPO investor in AI-powered advertising technology company AppLovin, which went public on the Nasdaq in 2021.",
    "He owns 2% of AppLovin and has served on the company's board of directors since 2018.",
    "Vivas is one of eight billionaires from AppLovin, including the company's cofounder and CEO Adam Foroughi.",
    "Vivas tookover as COO of social shopping startup Humans, Inc. in 2024, when it acquired Curated, the online outdoor sports retailer Vivas cofounded in 2017. Humans shutdown in 2025.",
    "Vivas previously served as head of product and talent solutions at LinkedIn from 2014 to 2017, after the company acquired Bright.com, which Vivas cofounded in 2011."
